      "slides": [
        {
          "menuItem": "Introduction",
          "title": "Fun at Parties",
          "body": "<p>Fun at Parties is a mobile app that allows you to select, personalize and send digital versions of real, interactive greeting cards to your recipient via email, text msg., Facebook or Twitter.</p><p>The interactive cards in the Fun at Parties collection include cards with sound, movement, and lights. You can personalize the inside of the card with a photo, personal message, digital signature, and in some cases, a recordable voice message.</p><p>Your recipient will receive a link that when clicked, will present your card and allow them to interact with it in a variety of ways. They can open the card with their finger like a real greeting card, and view your personalizations.</p><p>Depending on the card, they may be prompted to tap on the card to trigger some of the movements or sounds, including songs, your recorded greetings, bodily noises or other silly things. Some cards will play the sounds when the card is opened.</p>",
          "forward": "Dive In!"
        }
      ]
    },
